      "comment": "DISTINCTION (8) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at Horsham in a handy 26.77 beating Doongalla Don. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can measure up again. MAV REIKO (7) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Special conditions H winner three back (30.00) at Geelong over 520m. Can turn it around this time. PAW WAVERLY (1) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (29.09) at Sale. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. PAW NIMBUS (2) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
